Text: VERIZON CELLULAR HOLIDAY SPECIALCellular representatives are pleased to announce a cellular holiday special involving Enron employees Demos will consist of the new digital series latest price plans and a new phone upgrade program from analog to digital This event is scheduled for Thursday November AMPM in room Stop by anytime during this time frame say hello to Amy Pick our new Verizon Cellular representative involving Enron Happy holidays Tammy Anderson Telecommunications
